---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import horissImg from '../assets/Horiss logo.jpg';
---

<Layout>
	<section class="page">
		<h1>About</h1>
		<p>Creative Learning Haven (CLH) runs 2 community libraries in Ugandaâ€™s Imvepi and Rhino refugee camps since January 2025.</p>
		<p>These additional learning spaces are the first of their kind in the camps.</p>
		<p style="margin-top: 40px;">Our project is run by Lulu Tian and 2 refugee-led organizations:</p>

		<div class="orgs">
			<div class="org">
				<img src={horissImg.src} alt="Hope Rising South Sudan" />
			</div>
			<div class="org tbd">Lulu what is the other org</div>
		</div>

		<a class="support-btn recolor-on-hover" href="/support-us">SUPPORT US TODAY</a>
	</section>
</Layout>

<style>
	.page {
		max-width: 500px;
		margin: 32px auto;
		padding: 0 16px;
		text-align: center;
	}

	h1 { color: var(--color-hover); margin-bottom: 12px; margin-top: 100px; text-align: center; }

	p { margin: 8px auto; line-height: 1.6; text-align: justify; }

	.orgs {
		margin-top: 40px;
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr));
		gap: 12px;
	}

	.org {
		place-items: center;
	}

	.org img { width: 90%; height: 90%; object-fit: contain; }

	.org.tbd { color: var(--color-ink); font-weight: 800; letter-spacing: .06em; }

	.support-btn {
		display: inline-block;
		margin: 28px auto 0;
		padding: 12px 32px;
		border-radius: 999px;
		text-decoration: none;
		font-size: 0.8rem;
		font-family: 'Avenir Custom', Avenir, Inter, system-ui, -apple-system, Segoe UI, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif;
		font-weight: 300;
		color: var(--color-white);
		background: var(--color-subscribe-dark);
	}
</style>


